    // Posts
    section.section-98.section-sm-110.bg-lilac.text-xs-left
      .shell
        .range.range-xs-center
          .cell-lg-8
            // News Post
            article.news-post
              .unit.unit-xs.unit-xs-horizontal.unit-spacing-lg
                .unit-left
                  .post-meta
                    h6.text-italic.text-primary 2009
                .unit-body
                  .inset-lg-left-20
                    h5 Bestselling Author
                    p.text-dark John is a #1 New York Times bestselling author. With more than 1 million copies collectively in print, his seven books on personal finance have been translated into several languages and educated countless people worldwide. The Truth About Money was recognized with an Excellence in Financial Literacy Education (EIFLE) Book of the Year Award from the Institute for Financial Literacy (March 2007), a Gold Medal Axiom Award (March 2008).

            // News Post
            article.news-post.offset-top-50
              .unit.unit-xs.unit-xs-horizontal.unit-spacing-lg
                .unit-left
                  .post-meta
                    h6.text-italic.text-primary 2012
                .unit-body
                  .inset-lg-left-20
                    h5 Award-Winning Host of Radio and Television Shows
                    p.text-dark John's radio show has been on the air for more than 20 years and is heard throughout the country, enjoying more than 1 million listeners every week. In 2011, John was named among the "Heavy Hundred" in the radio industry by TALKERS magazine.

            // News Post
